</li><li> In the animated series <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/MightyMax" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/MightyMax">Mighty Max</a></em>, bird-like scholarly mystic Virgil is constantly correcting people that he is a "fowl", not a "chicken".
